text: Hershell America (born 17 February 1994) is a South African cricketer. He made his first-class debut for South Western Districts in the 2017–18 Sunfoil 3-Day Cup on 15 February 2018. He made his List A debut for South Western Districts in the 2018–19 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge on 28 October 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:South Western Districts cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
